programme.desc: Joining us on this week's I'm LIVE is singer-songwriter producer rapper and DJ Peakboy! This artist first garnered the public's attention with his song Gin & Tonic on SoundCloud. Also taking part in other TV shows like Hangout with Yoo Peakboy is definitely securing his spot not only in the music scene but in the entire entertainment industry. Upon the release it ranked No. 1 in all music genres on the Hot & New chart for six consecutive days and also ranked No. 1 in the Top 50 music genres in the world with 25 million streams on Youtube. What's more it was covered by Grammy Award-winning Korean soprano Jo Sumi at her concert in Italy. As if to prove their status as a producer duo they have already won awards at multiple music competitions.
